      • getDefault

        MetadataFieldMapper getDefault​(MappedFieldType fieldType,
                               Mapper.TypeParser.ParserContext parserContext)
        Get the default MetadataFieldMapper to use, if nothing had to be parsed.
        参数:
        fieldType - the existing field type for this meta mapper on the current index or null if this is the first type being introduced
        parserContext - context that may be useful to build the field like analyzers
